    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, keeping it garage-stored and spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with a capital L, you\u2019ve found it. Come give it a spin, I promise you\u2019ll fall in love! \u2728",
