    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS system. This example boasts a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via the factory variable M differential. Mechanically flawless, the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure peak high-revving reliability. The chassis remains taut, showing zero bushing deflection or hydraulic leaks. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with no signs of oxidation, clear coat failure, or road rash. A true turn-key performance icon for the discerning purist seeking a preserved analog driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
