      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its flawless original paint and high-gloss finish. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, with supple leather, immaculate trim, and that distinct 'new car' scent. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive maintenance log included. There are absolutely no mechanical flaws, leaks, or cosmetic imperfections. This is a rare opportunity to own a turnkey example of automotive excellence, perfect for the most discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
