      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty. It\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the lot\u2014I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, you won't find a single scratch anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and honestly, I'm a little sad to see it go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy this pristine ride! It's been garage-kept and pampered since day one, so it's totally ready for its next big adventure. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
